<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 03:14:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>超强台风八木横扫中国海南省登陆越南</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/super-typhoon-yagi-sets-sight-vietnam-after-tearing-through-chinas-hainan-2024-09-07/</link><description>今年亚洲最强大的风暴超级台风八木在带来闪电、降雨和狂风后席卷了中国南部岛屿省份海南省，并于周六向越南北部海岸袭来。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 02:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/super-typhoon-yagi-sets-sight-vietnam-after-tearing-through-chinas-hainan-2024-09-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行8月份连续第四个月暂停黄金购买</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fourth-straight-month-august-2024-09-07/</link><description>周六官方数据显示，中国央行八月份连续第四个月停止购买黄金作为储备。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 02:40:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-gold-reserves-unchanged-fourth-straight-month-august-2024-09-07/</guid></item><item><title>8月中国外汇储备升至2015年以来最高水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-fx-reserves-rise-highest-level-since-2015-august-2024-09-07/</link><description>周六官方数据显示，中国8月份外汇储备升至逾8-1/2年以来的最高水平，这在很大程度上得益于美元普遍走软。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 02:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/china-fx-reserves-rise-highest-level-since-2015-august-2024-09-07/</guid></item><item><title>出于对军事关系的担忧，佐治亚理工学院将终止与中国的合作关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/georgia-tech-end-china-partnerships-following-concerns-over-military-ties-2024-09-06/</link><description>美国佐治亚理工学院周五表示，在美国国会对其与据称与中国军方有联系的实体的合作进行审查后，该校将终止其在中国天津和深圳的研究和教育合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 21:47:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/georgia-tech-end-china-partnerships-following-concerns-over-military-ties-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>独家：俄罗斯上调2024年石油、天然气出口收入预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-raises-forecast-2024-oil-gas-export-revenues-by-174-bln-document-shows-2024-09-06/</link><description>这些预期凸显了西方如何努力对俄罗斯经济造成持久损害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-raises-forecast-2024-oil-gas-export-revenues-by-174-bln-document-shows-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>奥斯塔彭科/基切诺克夺得美网女双冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/ostapenko-kichenok-win-us-open-womens-doubles-title-2024-09-06/</link><description>拉脱维亚选手奥斯塔彭科/乌克兰选手柳德米拉·基切诺克周五在美国公开赛上以6-4 6-3击败中法组合张绍伊/克里斯蒂娜·姆拉德诺维奇，夺得女双冠军。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/ostapenko-kichenok-win-us-open-womens-doubles-title-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>立法者调查美国零售商是否购买了逃避关税的中国汽车零部件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/lawmakers-probe-if-us-retailers-bought-chinese-auto-parts-that-evaded-tariffs-2024-09-06/</link><description>据路透社周五看到的信件，一个由两党议员组成的小组询问六家主要汽车零部件零售商的首席执行官，他们是否从一家可能逃避美国关税的中国公司购买了产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 17:12:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/lawmakers-probe-if-us-retailers-bought-chinese-auto-parts-that-evaded-tariffs-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国警告美国企业注意香港业务面临的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-warns-american-businesses-about-risks-hong-kong-operations-2024-09-06/</link><description>美国周五就其在香港业务面临的风险向美国企业发出警告，称其中许多风险源于三月份生效的国家安全法。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 16:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-warns-american-businesses-about-risks-hong-kong-operations-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国情报官员称，俄罗斯RT试图将美国选民推向特朗普</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russia-china-iran-trying-influence-us-election-intelligence-official-says-2024-09-06/</link><description>美国高级情报官员周五表示，俄罗斯官方媒体 RT 正在利用美国和其他人士的影响力，试图说服美国选民支持共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普，而不是他的民主党对手卡马拉·哈里斯。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/russia-china-iran-trying-influence-us-election-intelligence-official-says-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国、降价和成本：大众汽车危机的根源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-price-cuts-costs-fuel-driving-volkswagens-crisis-2024-09-06/</link><description>虽然大众汽车面临的许多挑战已经困扰了一段时间，但最近的两项事态发展让情况变得更糟。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:27:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-price-cuts-costs-fuel-driving-volkswagens-crisis-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>立法者希望美国解决中国农业无人机带来的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-want-us-address-risks-posed-by-chinese-agriculture-drones-2024-09-06/</link><description>周五，十几名共和党美国议员敦促拜登政府解决中国制造的农业无人机的使用问题，称这些无人机在美国农场的使用构成国家安全风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:14:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-want-us-address-risks-posed-by-chinese-agriculture-drones-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车需求放缓，汽车制造商调整电气化计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-adjust-electrification-plans-ev-demand-slows-2024-09-06/</link><description>据报道，日本丰田汽车已将 2026 年电动汽车生产计划削减三分之一，成为最新一家因需求放缓而缩减电动汽车计划的汽车制造商。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-adjust-electrification-plans-ev-demand-slows-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>三十年后中国停止外国收养儿童</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stops-foreign-adoptions-its-children-after-three-decades-2024-09-06/</link><description>政府表示，中国将不再将儿童送往海外收养，这推翻了源于其曾经严格的独生子女政策的长达三十多年的规定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:50:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stops-foreign-adoptions-its-children-after-three-decades-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国特使表示，中美在本周的会谈中“缩小”了气候融资方面的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/us-china-still-have-some-differences-climate-finance-us-envoy-says-2024-09-06/</link><description>美国气候特使约翰·波德斯塔周五在北京表示，中美在气候融资等问题上仍存在“一些分歧”，但在本周的会谈中在缩小分歧方面取得了进展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/us-china-still-have-some-differences-climate-finance-us-envoy-says-2024-09-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国请求世贸组织与加拿大就关税问题进行磋商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-submits-request-canada-wto-consultation-over-tariffs-2024-09-06/</link><description>中国周五表示，已要求在世界贸易组织与加拿大就渥太华对其电动汽车以及钢铁和铝制品征收的关税进行谈判，同一周北京宣布计划对加拿大油菜籽进口进行调查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-submits-request-canada-wto-consultation-over-tariffs-2024-09-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>